Name: Rijnbar
Review Text: Visiting Amsterdam from Calgary and went in for a beer to find F1 qualifying was on. The lady serving and the man from Sweden who grew up with Borje Salming were very nice and race fans. Took my wife the next day to watch the start of the race. Great place, 1922 original and will be back if I return to Amsterdam.
